00:31:41,590 --> 00:31:45,610
<i>Maison de Kim Min Kyu, PDG de KM Financial</i>

313
00:31:45,610 --> 00:31:48,300
<i>90-24 rue Hoenamu, quartier Yongsan, Séoul</i>

314
00:31:58,130 --> 00:32:02,780
